2025-09-16	ver.0.1.18g
	* Fix the regression of --addr option handling (bsc#1249755)
	* Really abort the program if the open fails

2025-05-12	ver.0.1.18f
	* Allow to pass a client name string and omit a port number to
	  --addr option

2024-03-29	ver.0.1.18e
	* README and manpage updates
	* Send both MSB (CC#0) and LSB (CC#32) for bank selection in
	  alsa-seq mode;
	  there is a new option --bankmsb to keep the old behavior

